,"src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20082,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/12\/08\/fatwa-dislike-halal-haram\/","url_meta":{"origin":27542,"position":2},"title":"Shafi\u2019i on Fatwa: Scholars disliked to say Halal or Haram","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 8, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Shafi\u2019i reported: Abu Yusuf, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cI know our elders among the scholars would dislike to say in their verdicts that this is lawful and this is unlawful, unless it was clearly found in the Book of Allah Almighty, without needing to be explained.\u201d Ibrahim\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25785,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/01\/21\/shafiee-advice-private\/","url_meta":{"origin":27542,"position":3},"title":"Shafi\u2019i on Nasihah: Sincere advice is given in private, not public","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 21, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Muzanni reported: Imam al-Shafi\u2019i, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cWhoever admonishes his brother in private has been sincere to him and protected his reputation. Whoever admonishes him in public has humiliated him and betrayed him.\u201d Source: H\u0323ilyat al-Awliya\u0304\u2019 9\/140 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u0632\u064e\u0646\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0634\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0641\u0650\u0639\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064f \u0631\u064e\u062d\u0650\u0645\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0645\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0648\u064e\u0639\u064e\u0638\u064e \u0623\u064e\u062e\u064e\u0627\u0647\u064f\u2026